## âœ… Final Steps Recap

1. ğŸ”§ Bundle:

```bash
cat /etc/ssl/religare/religare.in.cer /etc/ssl/religare/globalsign-chain.crt > /etc/ssl/religare/fullchain.pem
```

2. ğŸ“ Update Nginx config:

```nginx
